body:
Well, after a week from being disconnected, I am back and ready to get my Avicore on. However, after about a month, Minecraft time will be cut back due to my determination to do well. You have to study year-round for hours a day to do well, and I plan to do so.
But, I just want to get it on. See you in-game!
